 Episode seven of B’Concept Network’s web series “Bad Gang” has dropped. “Bad Gang” follows the antics of five university undergraduates – Cassandra, Uriel, Nancy, Martins and Flex. It was directed and produced by Victor Opkala. The series features Shawn Faqua, Uche Nwaefuna, Deborah Anugwa, Becky Eloho, James Smart, Francis Onwuchie, Susan Pwajok, Stephen Damian and many others. Watch the new episode below:   The best Nigerian and African video content from around the web specially curated for YOU! 